
Simple Fitness App

-----------------

Weight Tracking

  - Week starts defaults to Monday (User can change)
  - When a user enters a weight
    - Check for a "Day" entry, create if needed
    - Check for a "Week" entry, create if needed


  Unlimited entries
  Averages
    Weekly
        Uses each single "Daily" entry
        User can customize starting week day
    Daily
        App automatically averages all daily entries
  Graphs


Measurement Tracking

Fasting Tracking

Food Tracking

Exercise Database

Workout Tracking
